title: Dosage Vol. 3 DVD - Rock Climbing - xvid
description:
This is the latest rock climbing DVD from Big UP productions.

Xvid video codec required (free - google search)

"Big UP&#039;s Dosage series is the definitive annual portait of climb&#039;s state-of-the-art. Volume III raises the bar with six Doses of maximum-strength action and inspiration.

Chris Sharma, Dave Graham, Tommy Caldwell, Beth Rodden, Ron Kauk, Klem Loskot, Tim Emmett, Jason Kehl, Ben Moon, James Litz, Melissa Lacasse and more..."
